summary: i’ve been thinking about how people call villaneve toxic and i’m going to go on a limb that doesn’t get said too much, i don’t...
body: i’ve been thinking about how people call villaneve toxic and i’m going to go on a limb that doesn’t get said too much, i don’t think they are that toxic. at least not for each other. if you compare them to a “normal” relationship they are but if you think about who they are as people they work really well together. when eve is with niko, that’s a toxic relationship, she is toxic for him and vice versa, bc they keep trying to change one another. villanelle and anna, from what we know, was a toxic relationship villanelle was toxic for anna and anna was using villanelle. if/when eve and villanelle get together, they truly get one another and accept one another for who they are and aren’t trying to change one another and that kinda makes them perfectly nontoxic for one another.
